text: Uruguay sent a team of 39 athletes to compete in the 2015 Summer Universiade in Gwangju, South Korea from July 3 to July 14, 2015. ==Football== Uruguay has qualified a men's team in the football competition. Each nation must submit a squad of 20 players, with a minimum of two goalkeepers.
